reviews.snippet:
Amazing Halal Wagyu Ramen with Great Hospitality!

I had an incredible dining experience at this halal Wagyu ramen shop! The staff and chef were not only kind but also funny, making the meal even more enjoyable. The food was absolutely delicious—the Wagyu was tender and rich, and the ramen broth was packed with flavor.

What really stood out to me was how thoughtfully they catered to Muslim customers. The prayer area was clean and well-equipped with an ablution space and prayer mats, which I truly appreciated. It’s rare to find such attention to detail in a ramen restaurant!

Highly recommend this place for anyone craving premium halal Wagyu ramen in a welcoming environment.
